mortgage loans and related investments the companys business is focused on originating or acquiring senior floating rate mortgage loans that are secured by a first priority mortgage on commercial real estate assets primarily in the office lodging retail residential and industrial sectors these investments may be in the form of whole loans or may also include pari passu participations within mortgage loans it also originates and acquires fixed rate loans and subordinate loans including subordinate mortgage interests and mezzanine loans the companys manager is bxmt advisors llcthe company originates and purchases commercial real estate debt and related instruments to be held as longterm investments at amortized cost it directly originates cooriginates and acquires debt instruments in conjunction with acquisitions refinancings and recapitalizations of commercial real estate in the case of loans the company acquires and focuses on performing loans that are supported by properties and portfolios the companys loan portfolio is diversified by collateral property type and geographic location including senior mortgages and similar credit quality loans the companys various property types that secure loans in the companys portfolio include office hotel retail multifamily manufactured housing condominium and others its portfolio is focused on geographic locations including the united states the united kingdom canada germany and the netherlands » full overview of bxmtn company address blackstone mortgage trust inc  park ave fl new york   ny    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation michael nash  stephen plavin  anthony marone  paul quinlan  douglas armer  » more officers  directors blackstone mortgage trust inc news briefblackstone mortgage trust prices public offering of convertible senior notes may   briefblackstone mortgage trust reports q earnings of  per share apr   » more bxmtn news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsspecialized re